# Feature Globalization
Tags: regression

Created by MehmetSerhatOzdursun on 02/11/2020

A user must be able to switch the language display on the website from Azerbaijani to English and/or
Russian, by clicking on the the “AZ”, “EN” and “RN” language links at the bottom of the landing page
     
## Switch the language
Tags: case1

* Go to "https://www.ibar.az"
* Click language "switch_button"
* Click "en"
* Check the language of the page is "English"
* Click language "switch_button"
* Click "ru"
* Check the language of the page is "Russian"
* Click language "switch_button"
* Click "az"
* Check the language of the page is "Azerbaijani"




